BEGIN_TEXT

Solve the following equations for \(z\):$BR
(a) \(iz\ =\ 4\ -\ zi\)
$BR
\( z\ =\) \{ans_rule(20)\}
$BR
$BR
(b) \(\displaystyle \frac{z}{1\ -\ z}\ =\ 1\ -\ 5i\)$BR
\(z =\) \{ans_rule(20)\}
$BR
$BR
(c) \((2\ -\ i)z\ +\ 8z^2\ =\ 0\)$BR 
(This question has two solutions, one of which is \(0\), find the other) $BR
\(z =\) \{ans_rule(20)\}

END_TEXT

ANS(Compute("-2 i")->cmp);
ANS(Compute(( 1 - 5*i )/( 2 - 5*i ))->cmp);
ANS(Compute("i/8-1/4")->cmp);

